494
00:34:59,888 --> 00:35:01,056
Aku pergi.

495
00:35:03,975 --> 00:35:05,560
Hubungi aku jika berubah pikiran.

496
00:35:06,686 --> 00:35:07,687
Baik.

497
00:35:08,980 --> 00:35:10,273
Bersenang-senanglah!

498
00:35:10,356 --> 00:35:11,441
Itu pasti!

499
00:35:53,066 --> 00:35:54,567
KUAS CAT LEBAR

