00:35:59,197 --> 00:36:00,198
Ini.

502
00:36:08,206 --> 00:36:09,249
<i>"Itu dia."</i>

503
00:36:10,750 --> 00:36:11,709
Sebentar.

504
00:36:24,514 --> 00:36:25,932
<i>"Di perpustakaan. Sekarang, ini."</i>

505
00:36:27,600 --> 00:36:29,310
<i>"Akalku sudah hilang."</i>

506
00:36:34,983 --> 00:36:36,192
<i>"Kau sungguh tidak ikut?"</i>

507
00:36:43,366 --> 00:36:45,076
Bit-na, di mana tempatnya?

508
00:37:04,888 --> 00:37:06,097
Kita bertemu lagi.

509
00:37:09,851 --> 00:37:12,979
Kenapa kau di sini?

510
00:37:17,233 --> 00:37:18,067
Sudah datang?

511
00:37:18,151 --> 00:37:20,695
- Ya. Aku masuk dahulu.
- Baik.

512
00:37:26,618 --> 00:37:27,535
Itu junior…

513
00:37:28,620 --> 00:37:30,163
yang ingin minum denganmu.

514
00:37:34,125 --> 00:37:35,251
Begitu rupanya.

515
00:37:36,044 --> 00:37:37,795
Lihat! Habislah kau.

516
00:37:40,632 --> 00:37:43,009
Lagi-lagi orang yang sama.

517
00:37:43,593 --> 00:37:44,469
Para senior!

518
00:37:44,552 --> 00:37:47,013
Apa kau muak dengan para senior?

519
00:37:47,096 --> 00:37:48,056
Tentu tidak!

520
00:37:50,808 --> 00:37:52,352
Namun, ada anggota baru hari ini.

521
00:37:53,770 --> 00:37:56,231
Jarang sekali dia bisa datang,
