523
00:38:03,196 --> 00:38:04,322
<i>"Park Jae-eon…"</i>

524
00:38:04,906 --> 00:38:05,740
Ya.

525
00:38:05,823 --> 00:38:08,826
<i>"Namanya Park Jae-eon."</i>

526
00:38:10,703 --> 00:38:11,996
Ekspresi apa itu?

527
00:38:14,290 --> 00:38:15,375
Kalian saling kenal?

528
00:38:17,460 --> 00:38:18,586
Tidak.

529
00:38:19,087 --> 00:38:21,923
- Aku baru melihatnya.
- Sungguh?

530
00:38:22,006 --> 00:38:23,424
Mereka bergantian cuti kuliah.

531
00:38:23,508 --> 00:38:26,886
