Na-bi jarang ikut kegiatan kampus.

532
00:38:26,970 --> 00:38:30,556
- Benar. Dia tak pernah ikut.
- Padahal kau datang.

533
00:38:30,640 --> 00:38:32,058
Hai.

534
00:38:37,313 --> 00:38:38,898
Ya. Hai.

535
00:38:38,982 --> 00:38:41,484
Astaga, aku yang berdebar!

536
00:38:41,567 --> 00:38:43,027
"Ya. Hai."

537
00:38:43,111 --> 00:38:44,237
Aku yang berdebar!

