587
00:41:11,259 --> 00:41:13,761
- Ini ikat rambut.
- Lepaskan.

588
00:41:13,845 --> 00:41:15,430
Ikat ke atas.

589
00:41:15,513 --> 00:41:18,683
Jangan terlalu keras.

590
00:41:18,766 --> 00:41:21,352
<i>"Jae-eon adalah orang yang menyenangkan."</i>

591
00:41:21,436 --> 00:41:23,229
Kau cantik.

592
00:41:23,312 --> 00:41:24,188
Jae-eon!

593
00:41:24,272 --> 00:41:25,273
Maaf.

594
00:41:26,274 --> 00:41:27,275
Lucu sekali.

595
00:41:27,358 --> 00:41:28,901
Cocok untukmu!

596
00:41:37,201 --> 00:41:39,412
Maafkan aku, tapi…

597
00:41:39,495 --> 00:41:40,997
Mau minta gelas?

598
00:41:41,080 --> 00:41:42,331
Bukan.

