00:42:12,153 --> 00:42:13,029
Malu sekali.

608
00:42:13,112 --> 00:42:14,697
Kau kesal?

609
00:42:14,780 --> 00:42:15,990
Dia banyak tersenyum.

610
00:42:16,073 --> 00:42:17,617
- Ayo main lagi.
- Apa?

611
00:42:17,700 --> 00:42:18,868
- Ayo minum.
- Apa?

612
00:42:18,951 --> 00:42:21,370
- Bukan apa-apa.
- Ayo. Minum.

613
00:42:22,371 --> 00:42:23,873
Milikku.

614
00:42:23,956 --> 00:42:26,292
Ayo bersulang.

615
00:42:26,375 --> 00:42:28,711
- Bersulang!
- Bersulang!

616
00:42:28,794 --> 00:42:30,713
Oper itu.

617
00:42:34,175 --> 00:42:35,259
Terima kasih.

618
00:42:41,390 --> 00:42:43,726
- Semua, mendekatlah.
- Ada apa?

619
00:42:43,809 --> 00:42:47,396
Siapa yang melakukannya
di ruang rapat semester lalu?

620
00:42:48,981 --> 00:42:52,109
Ternyata benar ada kondom
di tempat sampah?

621
00:42:52,193 --> 00:42:53,819
Menjijikkan!

622
00:42:53,903 --> 00:42:55,279
Di sofa, mereka…

