626
00:43:08,668 --> 00:43:09,502
Tak ada?

627
00:43:09,585 --> 00:43:10,795
Kau tahu siapa orangnya?

628
00:43:10,878 --> 00:43:12,463
- Siapa orangnya?
- Minggir.

629
00:43:12,547 --> 00:43:13,798
- Kau tahu?
- Siapa dia?

630
00:43:13,881 --> 00:43:15,174
Payah sekali.

631
00:43:15,258 --> 00:43:16,884
Masih belum tahu juga?

632
00:43:18,386 --> 00:43:19,262
Choi Min-u.

633
00:43:19,345 --> 00:43:20,221
Mustahil!

634
00:43:20,304 --> 00:43:22,765
- Dia pacar Jeong-a, 'kan?
