637
00:43:29,063 --> 00:43:30,648
Dasar bajingan!

638
00:43:30,731 --> 00:43:32,400
Membuang wanita secantik Jeong-a?

639
00:43:32,483 --> 00:43:33,818
Kasihan Jeong-a.

640
00:43:33,901 --> 00:43:38,155
Banyak wanita cantik yang berselera buruk.
