667
00:45:23,427 --> 00:45:24,512
Bukan juga.

668
00:45:25,930 --> 00:45:27,139
Aku mau ini.

669
00:45:34,021 --> 00:45:35,064
Kenapa tertawa?

670
00:45:38,651 --> 00:45:39,902
Karena kau menggemaskan.

671
00:45:42,780 --> 00:45:43,781
Jangan bercanda.

672
00:45:48,994 --> 00:45:50,371
Penampilanmu berubah.

673
00:45:52,623 --> 00:45:54,041
Hei, apa ini?

674
00:45:54,125 --> 00:45:55,960
Ayo bolos, kita bermain saja.

675
00:45:57,461 --> 00:45:58,504
Maaf!

676
00:46:03,342 --> 00:46:04,969
