684
00:46:39,503 --> 00:46:40,713
Lupakan saja.

685
00:46:41,547 --> 00:46:42,506
Memangnya kenapa?

686
00:46:43,007 --> 00:46:44,592
Saat itu, kau tak banyak bicara.

687
00:46:46,677 --> 00:46:47,553
Yang penting…

688
00:46:48,304 --> 00:46:49,638
lupakan saja.

689
00:46:50,723 --> 00:46:52,933
Jangan khawatir.
