690
00:46:56,103 --> 00:46:57,480
Tentu.

691
00:47:01,484 --> 00:47:02,693
Kau belum menghapusnya.

692
00:47:06,155 --> 00:47:07,114
Ini?

693
00:47:10,701 --> 00:47:12,703
Maka itu…

