697
00:47:24,423 --> 00:47:25,549
Sungguh?

698
00:47:27,968 --> 00:47:28,844
Aneh sekali.

699
00:47:34,058 --> 00:47:35,851
Tak senang melihatku lagi?

700
00:47:39,647 --> 00:47:40,648
Itu…

701
00:47:43,192 --> 00:47:44,026
Biasa saja.

